{
  "texts": [
    "The model iteratively proposes and optimizes prompts to enhance performance.",
    "Research shows that these machine-generated prompts often outperform those crafted by humans, particularly in tasks like zero-shot and few-shot learning, highlighting the potential of large models to independently engineer effective prompts.",
    "The prompt template of the Automatic Prompt Engineering is provided in Appendix A.",
    "Evaluation metricsIn order to comprehensively evaluate our experimental results, we have employed four distinct evaluation metrics.",
    "These metrics encompass two dimensions, each evaluating the quality of the generated explanations from a different perspective."
  ]
}